---
---
<section id="about" class="about-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-grid">

      <div class="about-text">
        <p class="section-label">About Me</p>
        <h2 class="about-heading">More than a student.<br/><span class="text-gold">A force in the making.</span></h2>

        <p class="about-para">
          I'm Kanav — 13 years old, currently serving as School Captain, and absolutely certain
          that the best version of any story involves someone who refuses to give up. Whether
          it's winning a debate, acing an exam, or finally beating that last boss level, I bring
          the same intensity to everything I do.
        </p>
        <p class="about-para">
          My friends know me as the kid who has a Marvel reference for every situation (they're
          not wrong). My teachers know me as someone who asks too many questions (they're also
          not wrong). I believe curiosity is a superpower — and I plan to use mine.
        </p>
        <p class="about-para">
          This website is my story — updated as I grow. Come back in a few years and watch
          how far this goes.
        </p>

        <div class="about-details">
          <div class="detail-item">
            <span class="detail-label">Currently</span>
            <span class="detail-value">Grade 8 · School Captain</span>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-item">
            <span class="detail-label">Location</span>
            <span class="detail-value">India 🇮🇳</span>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-item">
            <span class="detail-label">Motto</span>
            <span class="detail-value">"Part of the journey is the end."</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-skills">
        <p class="section-label">Core Skills</p>
        <div class="skill-bars">
          {[
            { label: 'Public Speaking & Debate', pct: 92 },
            { label: 'Academic Excellence',      pct: 95 },
            { label: 'Leadership',               pct: 88 },
            { label: 'Problem Solving',          pct: 85 },
            { label: 'Gaming Reflexes',          pct: 97 },
            { label: 'Marvel Trivia',            pct: 99 },
          ].map(s => (
            <div class="skill-item">
              <div class="skill-meta">
                <span class="skill-name">{s.label}</span>
                <span class="skill-pct text-gold">{s.pct}%</span>
              </div>
              <div class="skill-track">
                <div class="skill-fill" style={`width:${s.pct}%`}></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.about-section { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

.about-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 4rem;
  align-items: start;
}

.about-heading {
  font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
  font-weight: 700;
  line-height: 1.2;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
}

.about-para {
  color: var(--text-muted);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  font-size: 1rem;
  line-height: 1.8;
}

.about-details {
  margin-top: 2rem;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.75rem;
}
.detail-item {
  display: flex;
  align-items: baseline;
  gap: 1rem;
  padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.detail-label {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--crimson);
  min-width: 90px;
}
.detail-value {
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
}

/* Skill bars */
.skill-bars {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1.25rem;
  margin-top: 1rem;
}
.skill-item {}
.skill-meta {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
}
.skill-name {
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  color: var(--text-muted);
}
.skill-pct {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.75rem;
}
.skill-track {
  height: 3px;
  background: var(--surface-alt);
  border-radius: 2px;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.skill-fill {
  height: 100%;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--crimson), var(--gold));
  border-radius: 2px;
  transition: width 1s ease;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
}
</style>
